Commentary: Roach starts with a length ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it solidly off the front foot.
Back of a length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and defends it off the back foot.
Fuller in length, just outside off. Pathum Nissanka drives but straight to the cover fielder.
Good-length ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka shoulders arms to this one.

Sri Lanka and Pathum Nissanka are up and running! Good-length ball, around the fourth stump channel. Nissanka pushes it to the left of the cover fielder. Roston Chase there fails to collect the ball cleanly and concedes a single.
Length ball, way outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it through to the keeper.
FOUR! Glorious! Nissanka greets Holder with a classical straight drive! A half-volley, around off. Nissanka presses forward and drives it past the bowler to collect a boundary.
Length ball, around leg. Pathum Nissanka tucks it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Good-length ball, jagging back in from middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it off the front foot.
Length ball, around the fourth stump, curling away with the angle. Dimuth Karunaratne prods but leaves it alone in the end.
Fuller in length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne jams it out towards mid on.
Good-length ball, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne gets behind the line of the ball to block this one out.
Good-length ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka leaves it alone.
FOUR! Edged and boundary! Good-length ball, around the fifth stump channel. Pathum Nissanka prods to defend but gets the outside edge which runs past the slip cordon and into the third man fence.
Length ball, darted on the pads. Pathum Nissanka clips it to fine leg for a run.
Good-length ball, jagging back in from middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it watchfully.

Top effort from Nkrumah Bonner to save a run for his side! Fuller in length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it past cover-point. Bonner gives it a chase, slides and keeps the ball in play just in front of the ropes. The batters take three runs.
On a length, around middle and leg. Pathum Nissanka turns it to wide of mid-wicket for a single.
FOUR LEG BYES! Back of a length, around leg. Pathum Nissanka misses his flick and the ball brushes his thigh pad before going into the fine leg fence.
Much better from Holder! Good-length ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka lets it be.
Another ball, around the fifth stump. Pathum Nissanka prods but shoulders arms to this one.
Length ball, angling in from outside off. Pathum Nissanka does not offer any shot to this one.
Leg bye! Back of a length, around leg. Pathum Nissanka looks to nudge it to the leg side but misses and gets hit on his thigh pad. The ball rolls away to the leg side for a leg bye!
Fuller in length, way outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Good-length ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka sits back and steers it to third man for a run.
Length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it through to the keeper.
Full ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne prods and drives it towards mid off.
Good-length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back and shoulders arms to this one.
Another ball, fuller in length, around the fifth stump. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it through to the keeper.
Overpitched ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne squeezes it out towards cover.
Short of a length, way outside off. Pathum Nissanka hangs back and leaves it alone.
Good-length ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and dabs it into the deck with soft hands.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Pathum Nissanka looks to block but gets an inside edge towards fine leg. A single taken!
Back of a length, around leg. Dimuth Karunaratne clips it behind square on the leg side for a run.
BEATEN! Good-length ball, angling in from outside off and then shaping away just that little bit. Nissanka looks to block it off the front foot but the ball zips past his outside edge.
Length ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it off the back foot.
Good-length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it through to the keeper.
That came back in sharply! Good-length ball, around off and jagging back in. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend but he gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it towards mid off.
Fuller in length, way outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne does not bother playing at that!
Length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders arms to this one.
Back of a length, well outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Short of a length, just outside off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it off the back foot.
Back of a length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka punches it off the back foot towards cover.
Back of a length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka stands tall, rides the bounce nicely and punches it past covers for a couple of runs.
Length ball, around the fifth stump line. Pathum Nissanka prods to block this one but gets a thick outside edge which runs past the slip cordon. The slip fielder gives it a chase and keeps it to two.

NOT OUT! West Indies lose a review as well! Back of a length, around middle, jagging back in sharply. Nissanka looks to block but he misses and gets hit high on his pad. Holder puts in an appeal but the umpire is unmoved. Kraigg Brathwaite opts for a review but the Ball Tracker confirms that the ball was going well down leg so the on-field decision stays.
Length ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka prods to defend but gets a thick outside edge which goes past the second slip fielder. Jermaine Blackwood gives it a chase and the batters take two.
Length ball, way outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Good-length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward but does not offer any shot to it.
Fuller in length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to drive but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders arms to this one.
Short of a length, around off, holding its line and bouncing after landing. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it awkwardly off the back foot.
Length ball, way outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it through to the keeper.
Back of a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka sits back and blocks it to the off side.
Fuller in length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka looks to drive but loses the grip on his bat and gets the toe end of his bat as the ball goes over the cover fielder. The batters cross for a single.
BEAUTY! Length ball, around the fourth stump channel, shaping away late. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend but the ball whistles past his outside edge.
Good-length ball, around middle, jagging back in. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Short of a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Fuller in length, way outside off, holding its line. Dimuth Karunaratne does not bother playing at it.
A full-length ball, nipping in a bit. Pathum Nissanka stays back and defends it out watchfully. West Indies still persisting with the fast bowlers.
Fuller, on off. Nissanka presses forward and looks to defend it to the off side. The ball takes the inside edge and goes towards deep square leg. The batters cross for a single.
Comes back in sharply! Good-length ball, outside off. The ball nips in off the deck. Dimuth Karunaratne stays inside the crease and lets it go to the keeper.
A length ball, outside off, jagging back in. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders his arms.
Fuller, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne comes on the front foot and pushes it towards mid off.
Another good over by Roach comes to an end! Good-length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders his arms.
Back of a length, outside off. Nissanka watches it sail past him and into the keeper's mitts.
Fuller delivery, on leg stump. Nissanka stays back and flicks it to deep square leg for a single.

BEATEN! What a beauty! Jason Holder comes around the wicket. He serves a length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne sees the width on offer and goes for the drive. The ball though straightens a bit after hitting the deck. Dimuth Karunaratne gets beaten, as the ball zips past the outside edge.
Length, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Fuller, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it to deep mid-wicket. The fielder fumbles and the batters take two runs comfortably.
A length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne has no shot to offer this time.

FOUR! Nicely played! Nissanka welcomes Mayers into the attack in some fashion. Full and on off. It was a juicy half-volley for the batsman. Nissanka opens the face of the bat at the last moment and drives it through covers for a boundary.
A length ball, on the pads. Nissanka nudges it towards square leg and gets a single this time.
FOUR! Put Away! Back of a length, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back, swivels and pulls it through square leg for a boundary. Not a good start by Kyle Mayers.
On a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it to point.
A length ball, outside off, angling across the left-hander. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out solidly off the front foot.
Nice movement on this one! Beaten! A length ball, outside off. The ball nips away. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend it out but misses. The ball beats the outside edge.
On a length, around off. Nissanka stays inside the crease and defends it to cover.
Good-length ball, outside off. The ball nips away off the deck. Pathum Nissanka shoulders his arms and leaves it for the keeper.
On a length, outside off. Nissanka leaves it alone yet again, as he shoulders his arms.
Full and outside off. Pathum Nissanka comes towards the line and defends it out with soft hands. The ball takes the outside edge and goes to the man at second slip on a bounce.
Full-length ball and around off. Nissanka presses forward and defends it out.
Good-length ball, outside off. The ball nips away and gets some elevation off the deck. Nissanka shoulders his arms to this one. A maiden over for Holder.
Fuller, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne comes forward and tucks it towards mid on.
Good-length ball, angling across the left-hander. Dimuth Karunaratne comes towards the line and shoulders his arms.
FOUR! Dimuth Karunaratne gets his second boundary off Kyle Mayers. Full length, on middle and off. Dimuth Karunaratne gets his wrists into the play and flicks it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
On a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders his arms.
Swing and a miss! A length ball, wide outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne reaches out and looks to push it through point but misses. The ball bounces over the blade.
Length and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward and defends it to cover with full face of the blade.
Nicely bowled! Full-length ball, on off. The ball jags in a bit and stays pretty low. Nissanka gets his blade down in time and blocks it out.

FOUR! Nissanka continues to find boundaries. This one was a gorgeous straight drive, could not have asked for a much better shot. Full length, on off. Nissanka drives it down the ground. The ball goes into the boundary at long on. No stopping that one. With this boundary, the 50 run partnership comes up for the pair.
Good-length ball, around off. Nissanka hops and punches it through covers. The batters take two before the fielder cuts it out.
On off, Nissanka blocks it out watchfully.
Fuller, on the pads. Nissanka flicks it through square leg for a single.
Full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it towards mid off. He has not been able to find the gaps in this game so far.
Looped up, full and on off. Nissanka dabs it to cover.
Flighted, full and on middle. Nissanka pushes it to cover.
Quicker, full and on off. Nissanka defends it out watchfully.

EDGY! A bit of turn now for Veerasammy Permaul. Looped up, full and on off. The ball turns away. Nissanka looks to push it to the off side. The ball takes the outside edge and goes past the slip fielder towards third man. The fielder gives it a chase and stops it from touching the ropes in the deep. The batters pick three.
Looped up, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne puts his front leg across and defends the ball out with his pads.
Full, around middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it towards square leg. The fielder was quick to get to the ball.
Floated, full and on off. The ball turns in a bit. Nissanka stays back and tucks it to the leg side.
Tossed up, on off. Nissanka comes forward and pushes it to the left of long on for a single.

Chase comes around the wicket for the left hander. Floated, outside off. The ball goes not turn away. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders his arms, hoping it will turn away, but it spins straight through and goes past the off pole.
Touch short and on off. This time the ball turns away. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to the off side for a single.
Full and on off. Nissanka works it to short leg off the inner half, as he looks to defend it out.
On off, Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to cover for a single.
Loopy ball, around off. The ball turns away. Nissanka looks to defend it out but gets beaten by the turn. Nicely bowled.
Full and on off. Nissanka pushes it to cover.
SIX! BANG! Excellent use of the feet. Pathum Nissanka launches himself. Full and outside off. Pathum Nissanka gets to the pitch of the ball and smokes it over the long off fence for a maximum.
Tossed up, outside off. The ball turns away. Nissanka prods and looks to defend it out but gets beaten.
NO BALL! Veerasammy Permaul oversteps and the umpire signals a no ball. On leg, Nissanka tucks it to square leg.
Outside off, Nissanka leaves it alone for the keeper.
OH! Close! Looped up, around middle and leg. The ball turns away. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back and looks to defend it out but misses. The ball goes off the pads to the off side.
Full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it watchfully.
Tossed up, around off. The ball gets some extra bounce off the surface. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it to the leg side off the inside edge.
On off, Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to cover.

FOUR! Poor delivery. Full and on leg. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it through mid-wicket. The ball races away. Kyle Mayers gives it a chase and tries to pull it back near the ropes but his forward momentum does not get the ball back and it touches the rope. A boundary.
Full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne prods and defends it into the pitch. A good over by Chase. He goes some turn and bounce which looked to trouble the Sri Lankan skipper.
Flatter ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka cuts it to point.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Pathum Nissanka lets it be.
Permaul sees Nissanka skipping down so he drags his length back, around middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka drives it to mid off.
Just a tad short, outside off. Pathum Nissanka cuts it towards cover point and takes a run.
Looped up, around middle and leg. The ball turns in a bit. Nissanka flicks it towards fine leg for a single.
Flighted, full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne works it towards long off for a single.
Full and on off. Nissanka comes forward and flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around off. The ball turns in. Nissanka stays back and tucks it to square leg for a single.
Touch short and outside off. Karunaratne stays back and cuts it to point, but cannot find the gap this time.
Looped up, full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne eases it down to long off for a single.
Tossed up, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne skips down and works it to mid on for a run.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka pushes it to cover.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Pathum Nissanka cuts it behind square on the off side for a couple of runs.
Tossed up, around off. Nissanka blocks it out.
FIFTY FOR Pathum Nissanka! A top innings from him so far but he would be aware that the job is only half done! Floated, on a length, around off. Nissanka works it to long off for a run.
BEATEN! Tossed up, on a length, around off, turning away late. Pathum Nissanka looks to defend but the ball spins past his outside edge.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks this one out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it solidly.
Floated, around middle. Pathum Nissanka skips down and pushes it to mid off.
Flighted delivery, around off. Pathum Nissanka prods to block this one out.
Another ball, fuller in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka presses forward and is solid in his defence.
Flatter ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne rocks back and slices it past point for a single.
Nicely tossed up, outside off, turning away sharply. Pathum Nissanka lets it be.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and cuts it to point for a single.
Floated, on a length, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it off the front foot.
Fuller in length, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne steps out and works it to mid on.
Flatter ball, outside off, turning back in sharply. Dimuth Karunaratne hangs back and shoulders arms to this one.
Floated, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka skips out and pushes it to cover.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka presses forward and blocks it.
BEATEN! Flatter ball, on a length, around off, turning away just a little bit! Pathum Nissanka looks to block but the ball zips past his outside edge.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter ball, way outside off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and lets it through to the keeper.
Loopy ball, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Tossed up, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne prods to defend this one out.

In the air, just short of the fielder! Tossed up, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to flick, closes the face of his bat early and it takes the leading edge which falls short of the cover fielder.
FOUR! A half-tracker, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne rocks back and cuts it past cover to collect a boundary.
Flatter ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drills it to long off for a single.
Flatter ball, around middle, turning in sharply. Pathum Nissanka tucks it to short fine leg.
A juicy full toss, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne skips down and heaves it towards deep mid-wicket. A single taken.
Fuller in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka skips down and works it to mid off.
Flatter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it off the front foot.
A tad short, outside off. Pathum Nissanka rocks back and cuts it to point for a single.
On a length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne eases it to long on for a run.
Another ball, fuller in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka drills it towards long off to keep the strike for the next over.
Flatter ball, turning in sharply from middle. Pathum Nissanka tucks it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Tossed up, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks this one out.
Fuller in length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it past cover and takes one.
A full toss, just outside off. Nissanka shimmies down and eases it to long on for a run.
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne prods but leaves it alone.
Loopy ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward and tucks it to wide of mid-wicket for a single.
Another full toss, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne skips down and flicks it to mid-wicket.

A stumping chance goes begging! Tossed up, well outside off, turning in late. Dimuth Karunaratne shimmies down and looks to slog but he misses and gets hit on his pad. The ball rolls away to the keeper but Joshua Da Silva fails to grab it cleanly and Dimuth Karunaratne survives!
Loopy ball, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne prods and pushes it to cover.
Fuller in length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne nudges it to wide of mid on and collects a single.
Flatter ball, on off. Pathum Nissanka looks to defend but the ball takes the outside edge and goes past the slip fielder. A single taken!
Short and on leg. Nissanka stays back and pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
FOUR! Nicely played.100-run partnership comes up for the pair. Short ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne goes on the back foot and punches it past backward point. The ball goes to the boundary.
On off, Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it out.
FOUR! Freebie for Dimuth Karunaratne. Full toss, on middle and off. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it through mid-wicket and bags a boundary.
Looped up, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out to the off side off the outer half.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! Chase gets his man this time. The skipper could not replicate his innings from the first Test match. He goes back to hut on 42. This has brought delight to the bowler and it means a lot to the West Indies side, after what they went through in the first game. Chase draws the first blood. Looped up, full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne chips it back to the bowler. Chase keeps his eyes on the ball, moves to his right and holds the ball cleanly. Joshua Da Silva roars loudly after Chase completes the catch.
Full and on off. Nissanka plays it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on middle and off. Nissanka comes forward and pushes it to the left of short mid on. Bonner dives to his right to make the stop.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Full and on off. Nissanka pushes it through covers for a single.
Floated, full and on off. Fernando prods and defends it into the pitch.
OH!! Beauty! Looped up, full and on off. Fernando presses forward and looks to defend it out, but gets beaten by the turn on this one. Brilliant ball to end the over from Warrican.
Full and on off. Nissanka prods and blocks it onto the pitch.
Flatter and on off. Nissanka goes back and defends it with ease.
Full, around middle and leg. Nissanka comes forward and looks to flick it away but misses. The ball lobs in front of the slip fielder off the pads.
Full and on leg. Nissanka looks to sweep it away, but finds the fielder.
Tossed up, around middle. The ball turns in. Nissanka glances it towards fine leg for a couple.
Full and on off. Nissanka defends it to the leg side off the inside edge.
Full and outside off. Fernando prods and defends it to cover.

NOT OUT! Joshua Da Silva had informed the skipper that he did not hear anything, but the skipper went against it and it costs West Indies another review. Loopy ball, around off. The ball turns away sharply. Fernando looks to defend it out but misses. The ball beats the outside edge. Warrican appeals but the umpire says no. Warrican looked excited and the skipper took the review. The UltraEdge showed no spike as the ball passed the blade.
On off, Fernando blocks it out.
Aerial! Full and on off. Fernando presses forward and defends it to silly point. The ball was in the air for a bit. Bonner gets low to his right but the ball touches the ground.
On off, Fernando defends it out.
Looped up, on off. Fernando defends it out watchfully.
LEG BYE! On the pads, Nissanka misses his flick. The ball takes the pads and goes past the leg slip and the batters collect a leg bye.
On off, Fernando works it towards mid on for a single.
Full and on off. Nissanka eases it towards long on for a single.
Full and on off. Fernando pushes it to cover for a single. Play suspended due to bad light, the players might not return on the field. We will have to wait and see what happens.
Turn and bounce straightaway! Flatter ball, pitching on middle and turning in sharply. Pathum Nissanka plays it with soft hands past the leg slip fielder.
Tossed up, outside off. Pathum Nissanka looks to drive but gets the inner half of the bat towards square leg for a run.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the front foot.
Just a bit quicker, around middle. Pathum Nissanka gets behind the line of the ball to block.
Fuller in length, around middle. Pathum Nissanka skips down and pushes it back to the bowler.
In the air...but safe! Flatter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka rocks back to punch it. The ball ricochets off the thigh of the the silly point fielder and falls just short of the cover fielder.
Flatter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka pushes it to cover.
On a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka gets to the pitch of the ball to block it.
Tossed up, around off. Oshada Fernando clips it to mid-wicket.
Fernando skips down and tucks this full ball towards the short leg fielder.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Oshada Fernando chips it to wide of mid-wicket for a single.

A stifled appeal for LBW but the umpire is unmoved! Flatter ball, around off, bouncing and turning in sharply. Pathum Nissanka stays back and does not offer any shot. The ball hits him high on the pad.
On a length, dwon leg. Pathum Nissanka tucks it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Fuller in length, around middle. Oshada Fernando skips down and eases it to mid on.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka cuts it straight to the cover fielder.
Shorter in length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka punches it to cover.
Floated, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Loopy ball, outside off. Pathum Nissanka shimmies down and eases it to long off to rotate the strike.
Overpitched ball, around middle. Oshada Fernando squeezes it out past the bowler towards long off. The batters cross for a run.
FOUR! Too short and punished by Fernando! A half-tracker, down leg. Fernando rocks back and pulls it behind square on the leg side for a boundary.
Tossed up, around middle. Oshada Fernando skips down and clips it to mid-wicket for a run.
Floated, around off. Pathum Nissanka skips down and looks to flick but gets a leading edge and the ball falls just short of the mid off fielder.
Shorter in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka pulls it to deep mid-wicket for one.
Flatter ball, turning down leg. Oshada Fernando does not offer any shot and gets hit high on his pad.
Tossed up, around off. Oshada Fernando defends it with soft hands.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle. Pathum Nissanka keeps it out.
Floated, outside off. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the front foot.
Tossed up, around off, turning away late. Pathum Nissanka shimmies down and works it to extra cover off the outer half of the blade.
Tossed up, on off, Nissanka plays it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Nice shot! Short and outside off, Nissanka goes back and punches it through covers for a boundary.
A single now. Full and on leg. Fernando comes forward and tucks it through square leg for a run.
Looped up, full and on off. Nissanka prods and defends it into the pitch.
A single now! Floated, around off. The ball turns in. Nissanka flicks it from front of his pads towards square leg for a run.

FOUR! An appeal for LBW but the umpire says no and suggests that there was some bat on it. A full toss, outside off. Oshada Fernando looks to sweep but gets an underedge which runs past the keeper and the leg slip fielder and into the fence.
Tossed up, around middle. Oshada Fernando clips it to mid-wicket.
Flatter ball, turning down leg. Oshada Fernando hangs back and tucks it behind square on the leg side. It falls short of the leg slip fielder and goes past him. The batters take a couple.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Flatter ball, just outside off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and punches it past the diving bowler towards long off for a run.
Tossed up, around leg. Oshada Fernando paddles it behind square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Almost, chopped on! Flatter ball, around off. Oshada Fernando looks to defend but gets a thick inside edge and the ball bounces off the deck and falls just past the sticks.
Tossed up, around off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Jomel Warrican finally gets his reward! Huge wicket for West Indies as they break this partnership which was starting to look ominous for them! This was a flatter ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando stays back to cut but gets an outside edge towards the keeper. Joshua Da Silva takes a sharp catch behind the sticks.
Howout: c Joshua Da Silva b Jomel Warrican

Commentary: Flatter ball, turning down leg. Pathum Nissanka clips it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Tossed up, around off, turning in sharply. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
FOUR! Excellent use of the feet and what a way to get off the mark! Tossed up, on a length, around off. Mathews skips down and whips it past mid on to collect a boundary.
Fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews steps out and clips it to wide of mid on for a run.
A bit quicker, on a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka shimmes down to keep it out.
Tossed up, around off. Angelo Mathews gets to the pitch of the ball to defend this one.
Flatter ball, coming in with the angle. Angelo Mathews stays back and blocks it to the off side.
Flatter ball, turning away outside off. Angelo Mathews sits back and punches it past the cover fielder. The batters take three runs.
Tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the front foot.
A tad short, outside off. Pathum Nissanka rocks back but cuts it straight to the backward point fielder.
Flatter ball, around middle and leg. Pathum Nissanka works it to mid-wicket.

DROPPED! A very tough one for the short leg fielder though! Flatter ball, around off, turning in late. Angelo Mathews nudges it straight to Nkrumah Bonner at short leg who fails to gather the ball cleanly.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Angelo Mathews gets down on his knee and sweeps it behind square on the leg side.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews gets to the pitch of the ball to block this one out.
Loopy ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews sweeps it towards deep square leg and rotates the strike.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the front foot.
Flighted, full and on leg. Mathews helps it towards mid on.
Looped up, full and on off. Mathews pushes it to the left of the bowler. Joshua Da Silva asks Warrican to go down. The bowler does that to his left and stops the ball.
On off, Mathews keeps it out.
BEATEN! SO CLOSE! Tossed up, around off. The ball turns away. Mathews presses forward and looks to defend it out but misses. The ball beats the outside edge.
On off, kept out solidly by Mathews.

Full and on off. Mathews pushes it through covers for a single. He retains the strike. A good over by Warrican. The spinners are able to keep the batters in check here. A good start with the ball for the visitors.
Full and on off. Mathews pushes it to cover.
Flatter and short, outside off. The ball turns away. Mathews rocks back and looks to cut it away but misses.
Tossed up, on off. Mathews pushes it out.
On off, Mathews plays it back to the bowler.
Floated, around off. Mathews goes back and punches it to cover.
Full and on off. Mathews drives it to cover, but straight to the fielder there. A maiden over for Veerasammy Permaul.
Full and on off. Nissanka pushes it towards mid off.
Tossed up, around middle and leg. Nissanka prods and looks to defend it out but misses. There was a lot of turn on this one, which beats the batsman easily.
On off, worked towards point for a single.
Loopy ball, around middle and leg. Mathews defends it to cover off the outer half.
Floated, full and on off. Mathews pushes it to short mid on.
NO BALL! On off, Mathews works it towards mid on. The bowler though oversteps and the umpire signals a no ball.

Jomel Warrican squares the batsman up here! Loopy ball, around middle. The ball grips and turns away. Mathews is squared up, as he looks to defend it out but fails to get any bat on it and gets beaten. The ball sneaks past the off pole.
Tossed up, outside off. Tad full. Nissanka stays on the back foot and looks to cut it away but misses.

OUT! LBW! Veerasammy Permaul strikes and gets the second wicket of the day. The visitors have started the second day on a positive note. Floated, full and around middle and leg. Nissanka prods and looks to defend it out but misses. He gets rapped on the pads. Veerasammy Permaul appeals and the umpire raises his finger after giving it a little thought. Pathum Nissanka asks the non-striker if he thinks it is needed to go upstairs but Mathews thinks it is not needed and Nissanka has to depart after a great knock.
On off, Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it through point for a couple. Dhananjaya de Silva takes a brace.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Brilliant work by Joshua Da Silva behind the stumps. Veerasammy Permaul picks up his second wicket of the over. What a turnaround. Flatter, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva stays back and looks to have a poke at it, he was very late into his shot. The ball takes the outside edge. Joshua Da Silva keeps his palms behind, but the ball lobs in front off him. He keeps his eyes on the ball and takes a one handed catch to complete his task. Brilliant from the visitors.
Howout: c Joshua Da Silva b Veerasammy Permaul

Commentary: On off, Asalanka watchfully watches it out.

FOUR! Charith Asalanka gets off the mark in some fashion. Full and on off. Charith Asalanka reverse sweeps it through square leg. The ball races away to the fence. As soon as the keeper says the shot. He continues being chirpy and say's it is time for some T20 action now.
On off, Mathews defends it off his front foot.
Tossed up, on off. Mathews blocks it out.
Full and on off. Mathews defends it out watchfully.
Full and on off. Mathews blocks it out.
Looped up, full and on off. Mathews blocks it out.

NO BALL! Flatter and on off. Mathews goes back and punches it through covers. The batters cross for a single. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps. He has to reload the final delivery.
Full and around off. Charith Asalanka looks to push it towards cover. The ball takes the inside edge and onto the pads.
A single now! Tossed up, full and outside off. Mathews pushes it through covers for a single.
Floated, around middle. The ball turns in. Asalanka stays back and flicks it towards fine leg. The batters take a single.
Flighted, full and on off. Chandimal pushes it to cover.
Full, around middle and off. Chandimal defends it out solidly.
On off, Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out.
Full and on off. Chandimal keeps it out.
A dot now! Chase comes around the wicket. Full and angled into leg. Asalanka defends it back to the bowler.
Full and on off. Asalanka presses forward and blocks it to the off side.
Tossed up, full and on off. Asalanka blocks it towards point off the outer half.
FOUR! The debutant is looking confident. Full, around middle and leg. Asalanka lunges forward and slog-sweeps it through mid-wicket for a boundary.

Short and around off. Asalanka goes back and punches it through covers for a single. A poor delivery to follow with. This has been the weak-point of the West Indies bowlers. They have failed to maintain the pressure.
Floated, around off. Chandimal punches it through covers for a couple of runs. Easy pickings.
Full and outside off. Asalanka prods and blocks it out.
Looped up, full and outside off. Asalanka continues to remain solid in his defense.
Flatter and on off. Asalanka blocks it to short leg fielder.
Around off. Asalanka comes inside the line and nudges it to square leg.
On the pads, Asalanka tucks it to square leg.

OUT! CAUGHT! Simple catch to short leg and the spinners are working their magic for the visitors. Veerasammy Permaul picks up his third wicket. Looped up, around off. The ball grips and turns in. Charith Asalanka prods and looks to defend it out. The ball takes the inside edge, goes onto the pads and lobs towards short leg. Nkrumah Bonner is stationed there and he takes a simple catch, with his eyes on the ball. Sri Lanka slip further.
Howout: c Nkrumah Bonner b Veerasammy Permaul

Commentary: DROPPED! Full and on off. Dinesh Chandimal looks to defend it out. The ball turns away. The ball takes the outside edge and goes towards first slip. The ball lands short of the fielder.

Oh Dear! Joshua Da Silva will be unhappy that he put his gloves in between. Looped up, full and on off. The ball turns away. Dinesh Chandimal looks to defend it out. The ball takes the outside edge. Joshua Da Silva pushes his hand to the right and looks to grab it but the ball defelects and goes to the off side. It was an easy catch for the slip fielder.

OUT! LBW! Jomel Warrican strikes and gets his second wicket. Full, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal gets low and looks to sweep it away but misses. The ball sneaks under the blade and raps him on the pads. Jomel Warrican appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Dinesh Chandimal opts for the review. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. The Ball Tracker shows three reds and the batter has to trudge back to the pavilion.
Full and on off. Lakmal presses forward and defends it out.
Slower through the air, around off. Lakmal prods and looks to defend it out. The ball turns away and beats the outside edge.
FOUR! All runs coming from this point are crucial for the hosts. Short and on off. Lakmal stays back and pulls it over mid-wicket for a boundary. A poor delivery to end a good over by Warrican.
Flatter and on off. Mendis stays back and punches it to point.
Tossed up, on off. Mendis defends it out solidly.
FOUR! Now Mendis gets off the mark with a boundary. Full and on off. Mendis gets low and sweeps it through square leg. His shot almost gets the square leg umpire. The ball races away to the fence.
Full and on off. Mendis goes for the sweep again. This time it hits Nkrumah Bonner on his shin pads and short leg and saves a boundary.
Floated, full and outside out. The ball turns away. Mendis leaves it alone.
On the pads, Mendis tucks it to square leg for a single.
On off, Mendis pushes it to mid off.
Full and on off. Mendis blocks it out.

OUT! TAKEN! A very soft dismissal and Sri Lanka slip further! Flatter ball, around off, turning away late. Ramesh Mendis looks to flick it to the leg side against the turn but closes the bat face early. The ball takes the leading edge and goes straight to Shai Hope at cover who takes a dolly.
Howout: c Shai Hope b Jomel Warrican

Commentary: Flatter ball, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it off the front foot.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to defend but gets the inside edge which falls just wide of Nkrumah Bonner at short leg.
Fuller in length, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter ball, outside off. Suranga Lakmal stays back and cuts it to cover-point for a run.
Turn and bounce! Floated, around middle and turning down leg. Lasith Embuldeniya chips it to wide of the leg slip fielder for a single.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Suranga Lakmal looks to cut but it goes off the inner half towards cover.
Tossed up, down leg. Suranga Lakmal turns it to the leg side and rotates the strike.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya smothers the spin nicely and pushes it to mid off.
Floated, on a length, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya skips down and works it to mid off.
FOUR! Width on offer and Lakmal pounces on it! Too short, outside off. Suranga Lakmal rocks back and cuts it past point for a boundary.
Tossed up, on off. Suranga Lakmal blocks it out.
Flatter ball, around off. Suranga Lakmal defends it off the front foot.
Darted on the pads. Suranga Lakmal clips it to wide of mid-wicket and collects a couple.
On a length, outside off. Suranga Lakmal blocks it off the front foot.
BEATEN! Drift and turn for Warrican! Tossed up, around off, turning away late. Suranga Lakmal prods to defend but the ball spins past his outside edge.

OUT! BOWLED! Permaul is on a roll here at Galle! He hurls a full ball, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya stays inside the line of the ball and looks to work it towards cover-point but he misses and the ball crashes onto his stumps. What a comeback this has been from West Indies!
Flatter ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews cuts it to cover.
Shorter in length, outside off. Angelo Mathews drags it to long off and hops towards the other end. He is clearly struggling with his hamstring here!
On a length, around middle. Suranga Lakmal blocks it out.
Flatter ball, just outside off. Suranga Lakmal stays back to cut but does not get any bat on it.
A tad short, outside off. Suranga Lakmal looks to cut yet again but gets and underedge towards backward point.
Loopy ball, around off. Angelo Mathews drills it to long off but does not run!
Another ball, fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews strokes it to long on.
Just short of the long off fielder! Tossed up, outside off. Angelo Mathews lofts it towards long off.
Fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews drives it hard to long off.

SIX! BANG! Just over the long on fielder! Tossed up, around middle. Angelo Mathews clears his front leg and lofts it towards long on. The fielder in the deep jumps but the ball goes just over him for a biggie.
SIX! AND AGAIN! Loopy ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews middles this one as he smacks it over long on for another maximum!
Loopy ball, on off. Suranga Lakmal blocks it out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Suranga Lakmal cuts it to point.
Darted on the pads. Suranga Lakmal clears his front leg and defends it.
An appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire. Fuller in length, around off. Suranga Lakmal prods to block this one. It was clearly off the bat. Maybe the sound was of the bat hitting the pad.

OUT! TAKEN! Veerasammy Permaul gets a five-wicket haul and Sri Lanka lose their ninth wicket now! Loopy ball, outside off, inviting the batter to slog. Lakmal sees the flight and looks to go downtown but gets a thick outside edge which goes towards Jomel Warrican at backward point and he takes a simple catch.
Howout: c Jomel Warrican b Veerasammy Permaul

Commentary: Tossed up, on off. Praveen Jayawickrama blocks it.
Fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out watchfully.
FOUR! SMASHED! Loopy ball, in the slot, around off. Angelo Mathews gets to the pitch of the ball and smokes it past the bowler. The ball races away to the fence.

OUT! BOWLED! A peach of a delivery to get rid of the injured Angelo Mathews! Most of the batters would have found it hard to negotiate this beauty! Tossed up, around middle, and turning away just that little bit. Mathews prods to block, does not get to the pitch of the ball due to his hamstring and he misses. The ball spins past his blade and rattles his off pole. Sri Lanka are bundled out for 204.
NO BALL to start with, from Lakmal! A full ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite leaves it alone. The umpire signals a no ball as Lakmal oversteps.
Good-length ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it off the front foot.
Back of a length, outside off, curling away late. Kraigg Brathwaite lets it through to the keeper.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to square leg.
This is a full ball, angling in from off. Kraigg Brathwaite eases it to mid off with soft hands.
Lakmal errs in line and spills this one down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite misses his flick.

JAFFA! Good-length ball, around the fifth stump channel and nipping back in sharply. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend off the front foot but the ball sneaks through his bat and pad towards the keeper.
Tossed up, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out.
Fuller in length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood looks to drive but it goes off the inner half to the bowler.
Tossed up, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood drives it hard to the cover fielder.
Floated, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood defends it out.
On a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, around off. Jermaine Blackwood pushes it to mid off and takes off for a run. He gets off the mark now!
Back of a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it off the back foot.
Length ball, nipping back in from off. Jermaine Blackwood defends it to cover.
Short of a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood gets behind the line of the ball and pushes it to mid on.
Lovely delivery! On a length, around middle and leg, jagging back in sharply. Jermaine Blackwood looks to flick it but he misses and gets hit high on his pad.
Back of a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it off the back foot towards cover.
Good-length delivery, on off. Jermaine Blackwood keeps it out this time.
On a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out watchfully.
Tossed up, way outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods but shoulders arms to this one.
Flatter ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it off the back foot.
Flatter ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back and cuts it to backward point.
Sharp turn and bounce! Nicely tossed up, outside off, turning away late. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to poke at it but the ball spins past his outside edge.
On a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out watchfully. That will be Lunch on Day 2!
A couple to get the second session going. A length ball, on the  pads. Blackwood tucks it through square leg for a couple. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps.
FOUR! EDGY! A length ball, around off. Blackwood looks to defend it out. The ball takes the outside edge and goes through the slip cordon. The ball races away into the fence at third man.
Fuller, on off. Blackwood stays back and defends it towards mid on.
A single now! On a length, around middle and leg. Blackwood nudges it towards square leg for a single.
Full-length ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it to cover.
A couple more! Length ball, on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back and glances it towards fine leg for a couple.
Fuller, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it to the off side watchfully. 10 runs off the over. A good one for the visitors.
Looped up, full and outside off. Blackwood slaps it to cover but straight to the fielder.
Flatter and on off. Blackwood goes back and defends it out.
Around off, Blackwood stays back and punches it to cover.
Full and on off. Jermaine Blackwood prods and defends it into the pitch.
Short and on the pads, Blackwood tucks it to square leg for a couple.
On middle and leg. Jermaine Blackwood defends it out solidly to see off the over.
Good-length ball, around off, jags in a bit. Kraigg Brathwaite hops inside the crease and flicks it to the leg side.
A single now! Fuller, on leg. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
A length ball, on the pads. Blackwood works it behind square leg for a single.
On the pads again, length ball. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to the leg side for a run. He offers the bat at the last moment.
On a length, around middle. Some extra bounce off the deck. Blackwood flicks it through mid-wicket. The batters take two before the fielder cuts it out. He rides the bounce really welll here.
Back of a length, on middle. Blackwood ducks under it and leaves it alone.
Floated, full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it towards mid off.
Tossed up, full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite pushes it towards mid off and takes off for a single.
Angled in, full and on leg. Blackwood defends it to short leg off the inner half.
Full and on off. Jermaine Blackwood works it towards mid off for a run.
On off, Kraigg Brathwaite goes back and defends it out watchfully.
Flatter and on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite goes back and defends it to point.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Blackwood looks to push it away. The ball takes the bottom edge and goes through point. The batters take two.
On off, pushed to cover for a single.
Looped up, around off. The ball turns in. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it to the leg side.
Darted full and on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it to square on the leg side.
Floated, full and on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it back to the bowler with a straight bat.

A huge appeal for LBW but the umpire is not interested! Flighted, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite comes inside the line and looks to defend it out but misses. The ball goes to the keeper, after the ball brushes the pads. Mendis appeals but the umpire is unmoved. The skipper does not opt for the review this time. The replays show the impact was outside the line.
FOUR! EDGED! Full and outside off. Jermaine Blackwood throws his bat at it. The ball takes the outside edge and goes past the face of the gully fielder. The ball races away to the boundary.
A single now, as this is eased towards long on.
Full and on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and defends it into the pitch.
Full, on the pads, Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, full and on off. Jermaine Blackwood punches it to mid off for and gets a single.
Fuller, on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite works it to mid-wicket off the inner half. They take a single. A good over for the visitors, 8 runs off it.
Full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it to the leg side, but cannot find the gap.
On off, Kraigg Brathwaite works it towards long on for a single. The batters are doing well to keep the scoreboard ticking.
On the pads, Blackwood nudges it to the leg side for another single.
Full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite leans forward and helps it towards long on for another run. They are not letting the spinners settle here.
Flatter and short, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood goes back and looks to cut it away but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Slower, full and on off. Blackwood pushes it to mid off.
On off, Kraigg Brathwaite defends it onto the pitch.
Full and on leg. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, full and on off. Blackwood prods and blocks it out.
Full and on middle. Jermaine Blackwood presses forward and defends it to the off side off the outer half.
Outside off, Blackwood remains solid in his defence.
On the pads, Blackwood works it towards mid-wicket.
Full, around middle and leg. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, full and on middle. Jermaine Blackwood helps it towards mid on.
Full and outside off. Blackwood comes inside the line to defend it out.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off. Jermaine Blackwood pushes it towards mid off.

Just a single off the over! Fuller, on leg. Blackwood looks to sweep it but misses. The ball goes to the leg side off the pads. Mendis appeals but the umpire is unmoved. Dimuth Karunaratne opts to go against the review.
Aerial but safe! Full and on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend it out. The ball goes off the outside edge and eludes the short leg fielder.
On middle and leg. Brathwaite tucks it to the leg side for a single.
Full and on the pads, Jermaine Blackwood nudges it towards square leg.
Full, around middle and leg. Jermaine Blackwood prods and blocks it out.
Full and on off. Blackwood plays it back to the bowler.
Floated, around off. Blackwood helps it down the ground towards long off for a single. He retains the strike.
Full and on off. Blackwood blocks it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on off. Blackwood remains solid in his defense.
On the pads, tucked to the leg side.
FOUR! Nicely played. Full toss and on off. Blackwood steps forward and punches it towards long off. The ball beats the man at mid off and gets into the fence.
On middle, Blackwood defends it out watchfully.
Full and on off. Blackwood pushes it to mid off for a single. He will keep the strike again.
Tossed up, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter ball, darted on the pads. Jermaine Blackwood plays it with soft hands towards short leg.
This is spilled down leg. Blackwood misses his flick.
On a length, around middle and leg. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it off the front foot.
Tossed up, down leg, turning away a bit. Jermaine Blackwood rocks back to pull but he misses and gets hit high on his pad. The ball lobs up behind square on the leg side.
Floated, on a length, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood eases it to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood prods but shoulders arms to this one.
Flatter ball, on off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Jermaine Blackwood presses forward to defend it.
A tad short, coming in with the angle from middle. Jermaine Blackwood stays back to keep it out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood rocks back and punches it to cover.
Floated, fuller in length, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood is solid in his front foot defence.
Flatter ball, darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to the leg side.
Tossed up, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite stays behind and turns it with soft hands towards short leg.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it by getting behind the line of the ball.
Fuller in length, on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite eases it to mid on.
A tad short, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite hangs back and guides it past short third man to rotate the strike.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood prods to block this one out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite rocks back and dabs it to backward point.
Fuller in length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods to defend but it goes off the outer half of the blade to wide of point. A single taken.
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood punches it to cover.
Uppish but safe! Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood drives it uppishly past the cover fielder for a single.
Tossed up, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
A bit quicker and shorter in length, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite punches it to cover.
That was unplayable! Drift, bounce and turn! Tossed up, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood gets forward to block but the ball spins past his outside edge.
On a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood defends it out.
Fuller in length, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it off the front foot.
Floated, around off. Jermaine Blackwood keeps it out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out watchfully.

Top effort from Suranga Lakmal to save a run for his side! Tossed up, down leg. Jermaine Blackwood sweeps it behind square on the leg side. Suranga Lakmal runs there from short fine leg, puts in a dive and manages to keep the ball in play just in front of the ropes. The batters take three runs.
Tossed up, on off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it.
On a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood presses forward to defend.
Fuller in length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood is solid in his defence.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood pushes it uppishly back to the bowler.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out.
FOUR! CRUNCHED! Flatter and quicker, just outside off. Jermaine Blackwood rocks back and cuts it past the diving cover fielder for a boundary.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it by staying inside the crease.
Flatter ball, darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite turns it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around leg. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it behind square on the leg side.
BEATEN! Nicely tossed up, on a length, around off, turning away late. Kraigg Brathwaite prods to defend but the ball spins past his outside edge.
Darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite keeps it out.
Floated, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it watchfully.
Tossed up, around off. Jermaine Blackwood defends it out.
Flatter ball, around middle. Jermaine Blackwood is solid in his defence.
Shorter in length, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood punches it to cover.
FOUR! Excellent timing and placement! Tossed up, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood presses forward and drives it past the cover fielder for a boundary.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood punches it to cover.
On a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Shorter in length, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite guides it past short third man for a single.
A half-tracker, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood misses out as he hits it straight towards mid-wicket fielder.
Tossed up, on off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Jermaine Blackwood defends it out.
Tossed up, around off. Jermaine Blackwood presses forward to play a defensive stroke.
Tossed up, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back to punch it to cover.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods to defend but gets the outer half of the bat and the ball falls just wide of the silly point fielder.
That stayed low! Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back to cut but the ball stays low and goes off the outer half towards cover-point.
On a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets to the pitch of the ball and blocks it.
Floated, full and outside off. Blackwood lets it go to the keeper.
Full and on off. Blackwood defends it out.
Flatter and on off. Blackwood goes back and punches it to mid on.
Slower, on the pads, Blackwood goes back and looks to work it to the leg side but misses.
Full and outside off. Blackwood steps across and defends it out.
Around middle and leg. Jermaine Blackwood tucks it to the leg side. A maiden over for Praveen Jayawickrama.
Angled in, full and on leg. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out to cover.
Loopy ball, around off. The ball turns and bounces off the deck. Kraigg Brathwaite goes back and punches it to point.
Full and on off. Brathwaite offers full face of the bat and defends it into the pitch. A bit of a thunder now, lot of suspense from both end here.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it watchfully.
Full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and blocks it into the pitch.
Short and on leg. Blackwood flicks it towards mid on for a single.
Full and on off, defended out.
Darted on the pads, Kraigg Brathwaite clips it through square leg for a single.

OUT! LBW! Here it is, Praveen Jayawickrama strikes and draws the first blood. Loopy ball, around middle and leg. Blackwood prods and looks to defend it out but misses. He gets rapped on the pads. Praveen Jayawickrama appeals and the umpire agrees and up come the dreaded finger. Jermaine Blackwood does not think he is out. He goes for the review straightaway after the umpire raised his finger. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. The Ball Tracker shows three reds and the spinner finds the breakthrough.
Full and on leg. The ball stays low. Bonner stays inside the crease and defends it to the leg side.

Looped up, around off. Bonner prods and drives it to cover. A great over by Praveen Jayawickrama, a wicket and just two runs off it. Sri Lanka will try to use the momentum and make inroads in the game.
FOUR! Cracked! Short and outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite is offered width and he pounces of the opportunity. He goes back and cuts it through cover-point for a boundary.
A couple now! Full and on leg. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it through mid-wicket for a couple.

NOT OUT! Kraigg Brathwaite survives here and Sri Lanka lose a review this time. Tossed up, around middle, the ball holds its line. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and looks to defend it out but misses and gets hit on the pads. This was plumb, in front of tehe stumps. Lasith Embuldeniya appeals but the umpire says no. The bowlers convinces the skipper to opt for the review and he listens to the bowler. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. The Ball Tracker shows the ball is missing the stumps. The bowler cannot believe it. The on-field decision of not out stands.
Full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite goes back and defends it out.
Looped up, full and on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it.
Around off, Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out watchfully.
Full and on off. Bonner presses forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up, on off. Bonner pushes it to cover for a single. Poor from Lasith Embuldeniya who charged late on the loose ball.
Floated, around off, Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Tossed up, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it out watchfully.
Flatter ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite sits back and shoulders arms to this one.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods to block it.
A quicker ball, around middle and leg. Nkrumah Bonner stays back to flick but he misses and gets hit high on his pad.
Tossed up, around off. Nkrumah Bonner pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter ball, just outside off. Nkrumah Bonner blocks it solidly off the front foot.
Fuller in length, around off, turning away late. Nkrumah Bonner works it to the off side.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner defends it out.
Loopy ball, around off, turning away late. Nkrumah Bonner is solid in his defence. A maiden over from Lasith Embuldeniya!
Flatter ball, darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back and nudges it to square leg.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite lunges forward and blocks it.
Loopy ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and drives it to cover.
Lovely delivery! Tossed up, on a length, around off and turning away sharply. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend with soft hands but it goes off the outer half of the blade towards backward point.
Flatter ball, on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite gets behind the line of the ball to defend it.
Fuller in length, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite works it to cover.
Loopy ball, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner drives hard but straight to the cover fielder.
A tad short, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner rocks back to cut but finds the backward point fielder.
Tossed up, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner drives it to mid off.
On a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner blocks it out.
Floated, on a length, around middle. Nkrumah Bonner gets to the pitch of the ball and defends it.
Flatter ball, coming in with the angle and turning away late. Nkrumah Bonner hangs back and pushes it to cover-point. Another maiden over!
Fuller in length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it off the front foot.
Loopy ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite keeps it out.
A tad short, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays back and guides it to short third man.
Darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to square leg.
Tossed up, on a length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite presses forward and blocks it.
First run of the morning for West Indies! Loopy ball, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite eases it to mid on and takes off for a single.
Tossed up, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets low and pushes it to mid off.
A tad short, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite rocks back and cuts it towards backward point.
Tossed up, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to mid-wicket.
Fuller in length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it with soft hands.
Nicely tossed up, on a length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out with ease.
FOUR! Cut away! A half-tracker, outside off, turning away late. Kraigg Brathwaite rocks back and cuts it past the cover-point fielder to collect the first boundary of the day.
Fuller, outside off, spins away, watchfully left alone by Nkrumah Bonner.
Around off, fuller, driven but it hits the player at silly point.
FOUR! That was a poor ball and Bonner does not let it go unpunished. Short, sliding down the leg side, Nkrumah Bonner goes back and hammers this over square leg for a boundary.
On middle, pushed to covers.
Again, Nkrumah Bonner brings out the drive but only manages to find the cover fielder.
Darted on off and middle, NB presses forward and blocks.
Outside off, fuller, dabbed behind point now.
On middle and leg, nicely defended back to the bowler.
Fuller, on middle, spinning away, KB lunges and defends.
Floated, on off, KB blocks again.
FOUR! Very well played. Fuller, floats it up, around off, Kraigg Brathwaite uses his wrists this time and works this through mid on. The player gives it a chase but the ball speeds away to the ropes.

FOUR! Another boundary and Kraigg Brathwaite continues to keep the scoreboard ticking! A juicy full toss, around off, Kraigg Brathwaite steps out and whips this one through mid-wicket. The chase is on between the ball and the player and the former wins again.
Quicker, shorter, on middle, Nkrumah Bonner squeezes this one through square leg for one.
Flatter, outside off, the ball spins away as Kraigg Brathwaite looks to block inside the line and misses.
Around off, hit to mid on.
Outside off, Kraigg Brathwaite watches it closely and leaves it.

FOUR! Kraigg Brathwaite is on a roll here! Praveen Jayawickrama serves this short and on the pads, Kraigg Brathwaite waits and then works this one through square leg with some power and the ball finds the ropes.
On off, defended.
Flatter, on the pads, knocked through square leg for one.
Fuller, on off, hit down to long on for one.
FOUR! Not the best start from Mendis here. A poor ball, as this was flatter and on the pads, Nkrumah Bonner swivels and powers this through square leg for a boundary.
On middle and leg, Nkrumah Bonner looks to flick but misses and gets hit on the pad.
On middle, clipped to square leg.
Fuller, around off, hit back to the bowler.
Flatter and on middle, swatted to the leg side for a single.
Slower, fuller, outside off, no shot offered.
Tossed up, outside off, Nkrumah Bonner pushes this to covers and scampers through for a single.
Fuller, on off and middle, KB blocks.
Loopy, on middle and leg, Kraigg Brathwaite lunges forward and smothers the ball out.
The drive from Kraigg Brathwaite finds the cover fielder this time.
Shorter, around off, defended out.
Outside off, turned to the leg side.
On off and middle, tucked towards mid-wicket.
Shortish, around off, again, NB goes back and dabs this to the on side.

A loud shout for LBW but not given! This is bowled fuller, floated, outside off, Nkrumah Bonner presses ahead and looks to defend but the ball spins in and misses his blade, to ping the pad. An appeal but the umpire says nothing. There is a discussion but it does look like the impact might have been outside. The timer goes off and they do not go for the review.
Maiden! Outside off, pushed to cover.
Loopy, around off, KB pushes it back to the bowler.
On off, blocked.
Fuller outside off, kept out.
Angled into off and middle pole, Kraigg Brathwaite gets forward and shows off his defensive push away.
Tossed up, around off, Kraigg blocks.
Loopy, outside off, Kraigg Brathwaite defends.
Full on off, patted back to Mendis.
100 up for the Windies! Around off, pushed down towards long on for one.
Floated, on off, defended.
On off and middle, Kraigg Brathwaite turns this towards mid-wicket for one.
Drags his length back, short and around off, Nkrumah Bonner goes back, waits, and then blocks to the leg side.
On off, blocked again.
Tossed up, around leg. Kraigg Brathwaite lunges forward to block this one.
Flatter ball, on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and defends it.

FOUR! A loose delivery and Kraigg Brathwaite pounces on it! Shorter in length, around off. Brathwaite rocks back and pulls it in front of square for a boundary. The fielder at mid on gives it a chase but the ball wins.
Tossed up, on a length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it watchfully.
Tossed up, outside off, spinning away late. Kraigg Brathwaite does not offer any shot to this one.
On a length, around middlle. Kraigg Brathwaite eases it to mid on and keeps the strike for the next over by taking a run.
Flatter ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off, spinning in late. Kraigg Brathwaite gets behind the line of the ball to defend it.
Fuller in length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and works it to long on for a run. Ramesh Mendis dives to his right but the ball goes past him.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner drives it to deep cover for a single.
Flatter ball, outside off. turning in sharply. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets behind the line of the ball and keeps it out.
Loopy ball, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner drives it to cover.
Another ball, fuller in length, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner prods and eases it to short cover.
A tad short, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner stays back and cuts it to Lasith Embuldeniya at cover-point for a run.
Overpitched delivery, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to mid-wicket.
Darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite nudges it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner presses forward and drives it to deep cover for a single.
Sharp turn! Flatter ball, outside off, spinning in sharply. Nkrumah Bonner stays back to cut but gets cramped for room and pushes it to cover.
On a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner blocks it out.

Overthrows! Really sloppy from Sri Lanka! Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Bonner prods to defend but he misses and gets hit on the pad and the ball rolls to the off side. Mendis appeals but the umpire is not interested! Bonner looks to sneak in a leg bye and the fielder at cover has a shy at the non-striker's end but he misses. There is no fielder backing up and the ball runs to the fence!

FIFTY FOR Kraigg Brathwaite! Flatter ball, darted on the pads. Brathwaite tucks it behind square on the leg side and takes a run. A gutsy knock from West Indies' skipper and he has surely led from the front. The job is not done yet and he would be aware of that!
On a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner blocks it out.
Fuller in length, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner prods and pushes it back to the bowler.
Suranga Lakmal starts with a back-of-a-length delivery, around middle and leg, Kraigg Brathwaite misses his tuck and gets hit on the pad.
Around off, kept out.
Slightly straighter here, on middle, flicked through mid-wicket for one.
Back of a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner gets behind the line of the ball and blocks it out.

NOT OUT! An inside edge saves Bonner this time! Good-length ball, just outside off, nipping back in late. Bonner looks to defend but the ball takes an inside edge and hits him on his front pad. Suranga Lakmal appeals and the umpire says no. Dimuth Karunaratne opts for a review but the UltraEdge clearly suggests that there was a nick so Nkrumah Bonner survives and Sri Lanka lose a review!
Good-length delivery, around middle and leg. Nkrumah Bonner nudges it to deep mid-wicket for a run.
Overpitched ball, around off. Nkrumah Bonner pushes it back to the bowler.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner lunges forward and drives it to mid off.
An appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire. Flatter ball, around middle, spinning in late. Nkrumah Bonner looks to flick but misses and gets hit high on his pad.
Tossed up, on a length, around middle. Nkrumah Bonner eases it down to long on for one.
Loopy ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite presses forward and blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off, turning in. Kraigg Brathwaite sits back and defends it watchfully.
Short of a length, around off. Nkrumah Bonner stays back and defends it out.
This is a back-of-a-length delivery, just outside off. Nkrumah Bonner is solid in his defence yet again.
A bit fuller this time, outside off. Nkrumah Bonner shoulders arms to this one.
Length ball, angling in from off. Nkrumah Bonner presses forward and blocks it past the bowler towards mid off.
Change in length from Lakmal this time! He bangs it into the deck, around off. Nkrumah Bonner ducks underneath watchfully.
Fuller in length, around middle. Nkrumah Bonner tucks it towards deep square leg and collects a single.
Shorter, outside off, turns in, Nkrumah Bonner goes back and slaps this to covers.
Quicker delivery, around off, Nkrumah Bonner defends it out.
Around off, nudged to the leg side for a single.
Floated, on off, eased to cover-point.
On off, eased to the leg side.
Slightly uppish there! Tossed up, around off, Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend but the ball takes the inner half of the blade and whistles past the short leg fielder.
Good length, on off, blocked.
A touch shorter, around off, slapped through point for a single run.
Around off, on a length, pushed to covers and the strike is rotated.
On off, defended.
On a fullish length, around off, Bonner works this to the short mid-wicket fielder.
Short of a length, outside off, Nkrumah Bonner just dabs this one through point and takes one. West Indies are now behind by just 79 runs.
Darts it around middle, nicely fended back to the bowler.
Flighted, on off, blocked out.
Nkrumah Bonner eases this through covers and hands the strike back to his skipper.
On the pads, nudged to the leg side.
On the pads, worked to square leg now.
Outside off, shorter, Nkrumah Bonner waits and then steers this towards gully. An easy single and Bonner will retain the strike for the next over.
Good-length ball on off, Nkrumah Bonner's tuck finds short mid-wicket.

Around off, on a length, Nkrumah Bonner steps ahead and looks to defend but seems to hit the bat first and then pad. An appeal for LBW but the umpire says no. Dimuth Karunaratne is slightly interested but they decide not to take it.
On middle, blocked.
A bumper outside off, Nkrumah Bonner manages to sway away from the line of the ball.
The batsman has just watchfully blocked this out.

Was there any glove on that? Looked like it. Sri Lanka are not able to grasp this opportunity. On a shortish length, sliding down the leg side, Nkrumah Bonner looks to swivel and hook this one to the leg side. He does not manage to connect with his shot but only gloves this one, to the left of Dinesh Chandimal, who dives that side, catches it too, but the ball pops out this time. Replays show that this is off the thigh of Nkrumah Bonner and not the glove. Would not have mattered even if Dinesh Chandimal would have caught that.
On off, kept out.
On off, Kraigg Brathwaite pushes this to mid off for a run. The direct hit is scored at the non-striker's end but KB was well in.
Nkrumah Bonner has just blocked that from his crease.
On off, pushed back to the bowler.
On off, fuller, pushed down to mid off for a quick single.
Flatter on the pads, Kraigg Brathwaite dabs it to the leg side.
On a length, on middle and leg, Nkrumah Bonner misses his flick to the leg side and gets hit on the pad. An appeal but this would have missed leg.
That's very well bowled. A laser-guided yorker, on middle and leg, Nkrumah Bonner is ready for that and jams it out quickly.
Around off, kept out.
Full on off, blocked.
Outside off, on a length, pushed away to the cover region.
Good-length ball on off, kept out.
Tossed up, down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite plays it with soft hands towards short leg.
Fuller in length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite flicks it to the leg side and collects a single.
Flatter ball, turning down leg. Nkrumah Bonner tucks ie behind square on the leg side for a run.
Loopy ball, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite dabs it to the left of the short leg fielder.
Tossed up, on a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it off the front foot.

Just short of the short leg fielder! Tossed up, on a length, around leg, spinning in. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend it with soft hands but there is some extra bounce and gets hit high on his bat. The ball pops up off his blade and falls just short of the short leg fielder who dives in front to gather it.
Tossed up, down leg. Nkrumah Bonner gets down on his knee, sweeps it to wide of deep square leg and takes a couple.
Shorter in length, way outside off. Nkrumah Bonner cuts it to deep cover and collects a run.
Flatter ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Overpitched ball, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to wide of mid on for a brace.
Floated, around off, spinning away. Nkrumah Bonner prods to defend but gets a thick outside edge which runs past the slip fielder. The batters cross for a single.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite is solid as ever in his defence.

OUT! LBW! Ramesh Mendis gets the much-needed breakthrough and the Lankans are delighted! A flatter ball, on a length, around middle, going on with the angle. Nkrumah Bonner stays back to nudge it to the leg side while playing for the turn but he misses and gets rapped on his pad. Ramesh Mendis appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Nkrumah Bonner consults with his skipper and then opts for a review but the Ball Tracker indicates three reds and Bonner is a goner and West Indies lose a review as well!
Tossed up, around middle. Shai Hope blocks it out.
On a length, around leg. Shai Hope prods to defend it.
Loopy ball, on a length, around middle. Shai Hope tucks it to mid-wicket.
Flatter ball, spinning in sharply. Shai Hope gets behind the line of the ball to block this one.
Tossed up, around off. Hope is soild in his defence.
FOUR! Uppish but a boundary nonetheless! Tossed up, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite prods and whips it to the right of the bowler and the ball runs to the long on fence.
A tad short, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite sits back and cuts it to deep cover for a single.
NO BALL! Loopy ball, on a length, around off. Shai Hope blocks it out. Lasith Embuldeniya oversteps this time.
Loopy ball, outside off, inviting the batter to drive. Hope looks to drive on the up but gets it from the outer half of the blade and it falls just short of the cover fielder.
BEATEN! Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Hope looks to defend but the ball spins past his outside edge.
Flatter ball, outside off. Shai Hope leaves it alone.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Shai Hope hops in his crease and pushes it to mid on.
Flatter ball, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite keeps it out.
Shorter in length, darted on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to the leg side.
Tossed up, on a length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite plays it with soft hands and dabs it into the deck.
Fuller in length, around middle. Kraigg Brathwaite pushes it to the right of the bowler. Ramesh Mendis dives there and prevents the single.
Flatter and quicker, on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Loopy ball, around leg. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it towards Dimuth Karunaratne, on the bounce at mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around off. Shai Hope blocks it.
Floated, around middle and spinning away. Hope keeps it out.
A tad short, outside off. Hope rocks back and punches it to the silly point fielder.
Well bowled! Tossed up, on a length, around off and spinning away late. Hope sits back to defend but the ball spins past his blade.
On a length, on middle. Shai Hope blocks it out.
BEATEN! Floated, outside off and turning away from the batter. Shai Hope looks to defend but the ball goes past his outside edge. Dinesh Chandimal whips the bails off but Hope had his feet grounded.
Flatter ball, on middle. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it off the front foot.
Overpitched ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite eases it to long on for a run.
A low full toss, around off. Shai Hope squeezes it out to mid-wicket.
Short ball, around middle. Shai Hope rocks back and pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, around middle and going on with the angle. Kraigg Brathwaite prods to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards backward point.
Flatter ball, around middle and leg. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to wide of short leg. That will be Lunch on Day 3.
NO BALL! Tossed up, outside off. Shai Hope pushes it to mid off. Lasith Embuldeniya oversteps this time and hence, has been called a no ball.
