This one is banged in, but well outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya with an easy leave.
Loopy ball, on middle and leg. De Silva paddles it to fine leg for a couple.
Loopy ball, on the pads. De Silva misses his glance.
Tossed up, on middle and leg. Worked past mid-wicket for one.
Loopy ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya comes down the track and pushes it to cover.
Full and outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets the inside edge while looking to block.
Full ball, outside off. Blocked out.
On a length, on off. Blocked out.
Short of a length, outside off. De Silva comes down the track and punches it to short cover.
Full and on the pads. Dhananjaya de Silva misses the flick.
Short of a length, outside off. Tapped to the gully fielder.
Length ball, down the leg side. De Silva misses the flick.
Short of a length, outside off. Punched to deep point for one.
FOUR! Pulled away! Short and down the leg side. De Silva pulls it down to the fine leg fence.
Short ball, on off. Pulled to deep square leg for one.
Length ball, angling across off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to block but gets no bat on it.
Full ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya is beaten yet again as he looks to block.
Length ball, around off. Blocked out point.
Length ball, on middle and leg. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it.
Length ball, on the pads. De Silva looks to flick but gets hit on the pads. The ball rolls to deep square leg and a single is taken.
Length ball, just outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets the outside edge towards gully.

Beaten! Roach serves a length ball, in the corridor of uncertainty. Lasith Embuldeniya is lucky not to get any bat on it. Well, it turns that it wouldn't have mattered since Roach had overstepped. No ball.
On a length, on off. Blocked out.
On a length, outside off. Blocked out with ease by Lasith Embuldeniya.
Short ball, down the leg side. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to pull it away but gets no bat on it.
Short ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya ducks under it. Wide called.
On a length, around off. Blocked out.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Length ball, on middle and leg. De Silva works it to deep square leg for one.
A sharp bouncer, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya ducks under it.
Short again, outside off. Left alone.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Short of a length, lands on off and comes back in. Lasith Embuldeniya stays in his crease and blocks it.
Darted, on the pads, Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Floated and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it towards cover for a single. The fielder runs towards the ball but fumbles which gets rid of the pressure.
On off, Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Short and outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya goes back and cuts it through covers for a run.
Flighted, full and on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it to cover with soft hands.
A length ball, around middle and off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it to cover off the outer half.
BEATEN! A good-length ball, around off, going across the left-hander. Lasith Embuldeniya stays back and looks to defend it but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.

BEAUTY! Again beating the outside edge. All Lasith Embuldeniya can provide is a smile. A length ball, angling across the batter. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to push it away but misses. The ball beats the outside edge.
Full-length ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya stays back and punches it through covers. The batters take two.
Good defense this time! A length ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya takes a step forward and blocks it to covers.
Full and outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya punches it through covers. Veerasammy Permaul gives it chase and keeps it down to a couple of runs.
Slower through the air, on leg. Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it to the leg side for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out.
Loopy ball, outside off. The ball grips and turns. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to sweep it away but misses. Nice delivery by the skipper.
Slower and outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to chase it but misses.

BEATEN! Looped up, full and outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya comes inside the line and looks to flick it away but misses. He had no idea about the ball. Joshua Da Silva fails to collect the ball and misses out on a stumping opportunity.
On off, pushed out to the off side.
Full-length ball, on off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out in time.
On a length, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva stays back and defends it to cover.
A single now! Back of a length, outside off. Clipped to fine leg for a single.
SHORT! A length ball, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets an outside edge of it. The ball lands short of the fielder at gully, who is placed very close to the batter. A chance goes in vain!
Bouncer, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya ducks under it.
A length  ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out.
On middle, Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it to fine leg. The batters take a single and with this run, 300 comes up for Sri Lanka.
Looped up, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to chase it but gets beaten by the turn.
On middle, Lasith Embuldeniya tucks it to the leg side for a single.
Full and on leg. Dhananjaya de Silva looks to flick it but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Full and on leg. The ball clips he pads and goes down fine leg into the fence. It looks like it was signalled dead ball.
On off, Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it to the off side for a single.
Flatter ball, on off. Tapped to point for one.
Full and on middle. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it well.
Full and way outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya kicks it away.
Full ball, outside off. Another solid defence by Lasith Embuldeniya.
Full ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya goes back and taps it to the off side.
A very slow ball by Kraigg Brathwaite. A dilly dolly really, outside off. De Silva hits it to fine leg for one.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, wide outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets forward and blocks it.
Flatter ball, outside off. Lasith goes back and taps it to first slip.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Another one which is tossed up slowly, on off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, on off. De Silva taps it towards mid on. Veerasammy Permaul chases it and denies the single.
Flatter ball, on off. Tapped to covers. The man in the deep takes his time to get to the ball so the batters sprint for the second.
Loopy ball, around off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, on off. De Silva taps it to cover for one.
Flatter ball, on middle. Worked past square leg for one.
Shorter ball, on off. De Silva chops it past point for one.
Full ball, outside off. De Silva runs it to third man for one.
Loopy ball, lands on off and turns away. Lasith looks to block but gets hit on the pads.
Full ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to flick it away but gets the leading edge towards mid off.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, wide outside off. Driven to deep cover for one.
Darted on leg. It turns back in quite sharply and goes past de Silva's attempted flick.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Nicely bowled, just outside off and Lasith Embuldeniya offers a solid defensive push.
Nice and full, outside off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, on middle and leg. Blocked out.
Well bowled! Bonner tosses this legspinner quite well. He gets it to land outside off and turn back in. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to block but the ball hits the shoulder of his bat.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Floated, full and on the pads. Dhananjaya de Silva clips it to fine leg for a single. Now, the stand moves to 91.
Flatter and short, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya cuts it towards point.
Looped up, full and on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it to the off side.
Three dots on the trot! Swing and a miss this time. Tossed up, outside off. The ball grips and turns away. Lasith Embuldeniya gets low and looks to sweep it away but misses.
Full and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya comes down the track and pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya stays back and defends it into the pitch.

FOUR! 150 up for Dhananjaya de Silva. What an innings! He has made sure his side gets ahead in the game and absorbed all the pressure. Full and outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva drives it through covers for a boundary.
Floated, full and on off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it to cover for a single.
LEG BYE! Googly, around middle and leg. Lasith Embuldeniya comes forward and looks to sweep it away but misses. The ball hit the pads and goes towards third man. The batters collect a leg bye.
Floated, around middle. Dhananjaya de Silva tucks it to square leg for a single.

Tossed up, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets it towards square leg off the inner half. They take a single. The stand moves to 99. They are inching closer to break the record of the highest ninth wicket partership in Galle.
On off, pushed out but straight to the fielder.
Tossed up, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks defend it out but misses. The ball zips past the outside off.
Looped up, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it to cover.

SIX! Lasith Embuldeniya sets the record at Galle in some style. Full and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya uses his feet well here. Get to the pitch of the ball and smokes it off the middle of the blade over the long on fence for a biggie. This is now the highest ninth-wicket stand at this venue.
On off, kept out solidly.
Tossed up, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Full and on off. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it to cover.
Looped up, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it to cover for a single.
Tossed up, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya steps across and defends it to the off side.
Sliding down leg, Lasith Embuldeniya looks to flick it but misses.
On the pads, Lasith Embuldeniya defends it to the leg side.
Flighted, full and on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya stays back and blocks it out.
Flatter and on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya puts his front leg up and pulls it through mid-wicket for a single. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 4.
Full and on the pads. Lasith Embuldeniya works it to fine leg for a single.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, on off. De Silva pushes it to point for one.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out.
FOUR! Over mid off! Tossed up, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya comes down the track and hits it just over mid off for a boundary.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Length ball, on the pads. Flicked past mid-wicket for one. No ball called as Roach has overstepped.
Short of a length, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to pull it away but misses.
Slower ball, on a length, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya comes down the track to drive it but gets beaten by the lack of pace. The ball bounces and goes just over the off pole.
FOUR! Pulled away! Short ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya rocks back and pulls it to the wide long on fence. This is now the highest ninth-wicket stand for Sri Lanka in Tests.
Full ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya plays it nicely between the keeper and the wide first slip. Mayers runs to his right from third man and dives to stop it. Two taken.
Length ball, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to drive but misses.
Full ball, on off. Drilled down to long off for one.
Short of a length, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to cut it away but misses.
Length ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya taps it to deep cover and they sprint back for the second.
Yorker, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya digs it out to the gully fielder.

OUT! BOWLED! There comes the wicket! Finally, the stand is broken. What a knock by Lasith Embuldeniya though. He batted really well and put on a brilliant recovery with Dhananjaya de Silva. With that wicket, the declaration comes and that is the end of the innings. Full ball, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to drive it away but gets beaten and is bowled. Sri Lanka declare at 345 for 9!
Tossed up, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite drives it past covers and gets off the mark with a single.
Loopy ball, on off. Driven to covers for one.
Loopy ball, outside off. Left alone.
Flatter ball, on off. KB goes back and blocks it.
Tossed up, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out.
Darted down the leg side. Blackwood pads it away.
Flatter ball, on middle. Tapped to the leg side.
Shorter and on middle. Blackwood goes back and taps it with soft hands.
Flatter ball, on middle and leg. Blackwood gets hit on the pads while looking to block.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, around off. Blackwood drives it hard to mid off and sets off for one.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full and on the pads. Blackwood works it to mid-wicket.
Loopy ball, on middle. Jermaine Blackwood gets hit on the pads while looking to block.
Shorter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full ball, on off. Blocked nicely again.
A solid front-foot defence to end the over.
Full ball, on middle. Brathwaite looks to work it away but gets the leading edge to covers for one.
Shorter ball, on middle. Blackwood looks to flick but gets hit on the pads.
Turn and bounce! Shorter ball, lands outside off and turns back in! Blackwood is glued to his crease while looking to block but gets hit on the pads.
Wide of the fielder! Shorter ball, on middle. Blackwood looks to pull it away. The ball first hits his thigh pads and loops up to hit the bat. But it goes past short leg.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
FOUR! Beautiful stroke! Tossed up, outside off. Blackwood leans into it and drives it nicely to the cover fence.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full and pushed to mid on.
Short of a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite goes back and works it to covers.
Loopy ball, on middle. Pushed back to the bowler.
Another solid front-foot defence by Kraigg Brathwaite.
Shorter ball, on off. KB goes back, lets the ball turn and then plays it towards backward point.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.

Was there an edge? Nope, there wasn't. Flatter ball, around off. Blackwood goes back and looks to block but the ball goes straight and goes past the outside edge. The keeper fumbles while looking to collect.
Full ball, on middle. Blocked out well.
Darted on the pads. Blackwood works it past square leg for a couple of runs.
Nice and full, just outside off. Blackwood puts in a stride to block it.
Shorter ball, on off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on off. Hit back towards the bowler.
Loopy ball, on the pads. Blocked out.
FOUR! Hit hard! Lasith Embuldeniya gives this a lot of air and lands it on off. Kraigg Brathwaite comes down the track and hits it to the right of the bowler for a boundary.
Full ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Tossed up, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to block b ut the ball takes the shoulder of the bat and goes towards where a silly point could have been.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
Shorter ball, on off. Blackwood punches it to deep cover for one.

Just wide of short leg! Loopy ball, on middle and leg. Kraigg Brathwaite gets the inside edge while looking to block. The ball goes towards short leg. The fielder dives to his left but cannot reach the ball.
Full and on off. Blocked out.

OUT! LBW! Not sure why Kraigg Brathwaite reviewed that one! Full ball, lands on off and goes straight on. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to block inside the line of the ball and misses. The ball hits the pads and the finger is raised. The skipper of West Indies starts walking but then decides to review this. There is no bat on that, Ball Tracker has umpire's call on impact and wickets are hitting!
Full ball, on off. Bonner drives it to mid off and sets off for a single. The fielder throws the ball at the bowler's end but misses the stumps.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, around off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, on middle. Bonner uppishly plays it back to the bowler.
Nicely tossed up, on leg. Bonner is solid in his defence.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, around off. Blocked out.
Full and on off. Bonner gets low and blocks it.
Full and on the pads. Blackwood taps it to the leg side.
Flatter ball, on middle. Worked to deep mid-wicket for one.
A single as this is driven down to long on.
Flatter ball, on off. Blackwood goes back and blocks it.
Full and on the pads. Nicely blocked off the front foot.
Full ball, around off. Blackwood looks to drive but gets the inner half of the bat to long on for one.
Flighted, full toss and on off. Jermaine Blackwood stays back and slaps it towards cover but straight to the man.
Nice turn on this one! Looped up, outside off. The ball lands and turns away. Blackwood looks to defend it out but it beats the outside edge.
Full and on off. Blackwood punches it to short cover.
Big turn on this one. Floated, full and around leg. The ball grips and turns away. Blackwood looks to defend it out but is beaten comprehensively.
MISFIELD AND FOUR! Tossed up, full and on off. Blackwood punches it through cover. The fielder dives to his left to make the stop but the ball goes through him and into the fence.
Full and on off. Blackwood drives it to cover and gets a single. A good over for West Indies. 5 runs off it.
Full and on leg. Blackwood defends it to the leg side watchfully.
Floated, around middle and leg. The ball gets some extra bounce off the deck. Blackwood looks to flick it away but gets hit on the hips.
On off, Blackwood works it towards long on for a single.
Flatter and on leg. Bonner pulls it through square leg and picks up a brace.
On the pads, Bonner tucks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Blackwood defends it out watchfully.
Looped up, on off. Bonner works it towards mid off. It comes off the inner half, as he drags it from outside the off stump.
Much fuller, outside off. Bonner leans in and pushes it to the off side.
Full and on off. Bonner defends it back to the bowler.
Full and outside off. Bonner leans in and hits it through the line to covers.
Full and on middle. Bonner defends it into the pitch with soft hands.
Tossed up, around off. Bonner goes back and blocks it out watchfully. A maiden over for Praveen Jayawickrama.
Tossed up, full and sliding down leg. Blackwood tucks it through square leg and gets a single.
Around off, Bonner defends it back to the bowler.
A single now! Full and on off. Bonner eases it down to long on for a run.
Flighted, sliding down leg. The ball straightens after landing. Blackwood looks to help it around the corner but misses.
Full and on off. Blackwood remains solid in his defense.
Mendis gives it a little bit of air this time. Full and on off. Blackwood strides forward and looks to defend it out. The ball is aerial for a while but it falls besides the man at short leg.

A mix-up but safe! Tossed up, outside off. Bonner waits for it and guides it towards third man. The batters take a single. Bonner wanted the second run as well, he was halfway down the track. The fielder collects the ball and throws it towards the keeper rather than the non-striker's end, which allows Bonner to turn and gets back into his crease. He is not happy with Blackwood. Bonner says that it was his call, as he was running to the danger end.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on the pads, Blackwood tucks it through square leg for a couple of runs.
Full and on off. Jermaine Blackwood defends it wacthfully.
FOUR! Into the gap. Top shot! Tossed up, full and outside off. Blackwood satys back and punches it through the line. The ball goes through the cover region and into the boundary.
Floated, full and on off. Blackwood blocks it out solidly.
Full and on the pads, Bonner clips it to mid-wicket. Bonner wants a single this time but Blackwood goes against it.
On off, Bonner defends it out watchfully.
Full and on leg. Bonner pushes it towards short mid-on.
FOUR! Short and punished. Touch short and on leg. Bonner goes back and pulls it through square leg for a boundary.
On off, Bonner blocks it.
Sliding down leg. Bonner stays back and flicks it to deep square leg. The batters cross for a single. Bonner retains the strike.
Flighted, full and on off. Bonner strides forward and defends it out.
Flatter and short, outside off. The ball turns away. Bonner stays back and cuts it towards point. The fielder moves to his right and makes a good stop.
Full and outside off. Bonner looks to defend it out. He does it off the outer half towards off side.
On the pads, flicked to square leg for a single.
Full and on off. Blackwood prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
Full and on off. Blackwood remains solid in his defense.
Flighted, full and on the pads, Bonner stays back and nudges it to the leg side.
Full and on middle. Bonner comes inside the line and pushes it back to the bowler.
Around middle and leg. Bonner stays inside the crease and sees off the danger.
Floated, full and on off. Bonner plays it back to the bowler.
Around leg, Bonner remains solid in his defense.

Off the thigh I think! On the pads, Bonner looks to flick it away but misses. The ball goes towards leg slip off the pads, who fails to collect the ball and spills it out. Nothing much to appeal for now. A maiden for Ramesh Mendis.
Looped up, outside off. Blackwood lets it go past him to the keeper.
Much straighter, full and on off. Blackwood defends it into the pitch.
Floated, on off, Blackwood defends it out watchfully.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off. Blackwood blocks it to point.
Another maiden for Praveen Jayawickrama! Full and on off. Blackwood plays it back to the bowler.
Full and on the pads, Bonner clips it to deep square leg for a single.
Looped up, down leg. Blackwood defends it out with the help of his pads.

DROPPED! It was a chance and the skipper, Dimuth Karunaratne, fails to grab it cleanly. Full and on middle. Blackwood flicks it towards short mid-wicket. The ball stays very low. Dimuth Karunaratne dives forward and looks to catch it but misses, as the ball lands safely.

Tossed up, on the pads. Blackwood looks to defend it out, but looks like he missed it. The ball hits the pads and lobs to the right of short leg. The fielder goes to that side but fails to collect the ball. The replays show, there was no inside edge and the batter would've been safe.
Tossed up, around middle and leg. The ball gets some extra bounce off the deck. The ball rolls out after hitting him on the body.
Short and on off. Blackwood goes back and punches it through covers for a couple of runs.
Full and on off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Tossed up, around off. Bonner gets forward and blocks it.
Tossed up, lands outside off and turns away. Left alone.
Flatter ball, around off. Pushed to covers.
Loopy ball, around off. Bonner pushes it to silly point. The ball hits the knee of the fielder.
Full and on off. Pushed to short cover. Dot ball.
Short ball, down the leg side. Blackwood looks to pull but the ball his pads and goes to short leg. There is an appeal for catch but turned down.
Full ball, on the pads. Blackwood works it to deep mid-wicket for one.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full ball, angling across off. Bonner gets the outside edge but it drops short of first slip.
Darted on leg. Bonner looks to pull but gets hit on the pads.
Darted on the pads. Bonner taps it past short leg.
Loopy ball, on middle. Blocked out.
Tossed up, around off. Blackwood drives it to cover.
Full and on off. Pushed to cover.
FOUR! Punished! Short ball, on middle. Blackwood pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, on middle. Blackwood blocks it off the front foot.
Darted on the pads. Bonner works it to fine leg for a couple.
Full and on the pads. Bonner works it past mid-wicket for one.
Darted on middle. Blackwood works it round the corner for one.
Loopy ball, on the pads. Bonner looks to block but gets hit on the pads and the ball pops up to short leg. It is taken and there is an appeal for catch but turned down.
Flatter ball, on middle. Blocked out.
Full and on the pads. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, on middle. JB comes forward to block it.
Full ball, on off. Pushed to cover for one.
Full and driven to deep cover for one.
Tossed up, lands outside off. Blackwood leaves it.
Flatter ball, on off. Clipped to deep mid-wicket for one.
Loopy ball, on off. Bonner blocks it out.
Flatter ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, on off. Blackwood blocks it out.
Shorter ball, on off. Blocked back to the bowler.
Shorter ball, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood cuts it to point.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, around off. Bonner pushes it to mid off.
Tossed up, around off. Blocked out by Bonner.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Bonner blocks it off the front foot.
Shorter ball, outside off. Left alone.
Shorter ball, around off. Bonner runs it towards backward point for one.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, just outside off. Bonner blocks it right under his eyes.
Shorter ball, outside off. Bonner cuts it to point for one.
Full and on off. Blocked out by Blackwood.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, on the pads. Blackwood gets forward and blocks it.
Tossed up, around off. Bonner drives it to short cover.
Flatter ball, around off. Blocked out.
Short ball, down the leg side. Bonner looks to pull but gets hit on the pads. The ball goes past square leg for one leg bye.
Tossed up, wide outside off. Blackwood goes for the drive but gets it from the outer half. The man at deep cover gets to his left and keeps it to a couple.
Tossed up, on off. Blackwood comes forward and blocks it.
Shorter ball, around off. Chopped to covers.
Shorter ball, just outside off. Bonner blocks.
Short and cut away to covers.
Fuller, lands outside off and comes back in. Bonner stays in the crease and blocks it.
Full ball, outside off. Pushed to covers.
Tossed up, outside off. Worked to mid on.
Full and on the pads. Bonner works it to deep mid-wicket for one.
Nicely pushed to mid off this time.
Darted on middle and leg. Blackwood blocks it.
A solid front-foot defence.

OUT! TAKEN! GONE! Right at the stroke of Lunch! Tossed up, outside off. Tossed up, outside off. Blackwood looks to drive but gets the outside edge. Dhananjaya de Silva takes a sharp catch at first slip. That is Lunch on Day 5!
Howout: c Dhananjaya de Silva b Lasith Embuldeniya

Commentary: Short and outside off. Hope looks to chase it but misses.
Tossed up, full and outside off. Hope leans in and drives it to cover, but straight to the fielder. A wicket-maiden for Lasith Embuldeniya.
Full, around middle and leg. Bonner gets inside the line and tucks it to mid-wicket.
On the pads, Bonner clips it square on the leg side.
Floated, full and on leg. Bonner blocks it.
Full, around off, the ball turns in. Bonner defends it to short leg.
Flatter and on the pads, Bonner continues to block it out.
Loopy ball, around middle. The ball turns in. Bonner goes back and nudges it towards short leg.
Tossed up, outside off. Hope stays back and cuts it towards cover.
Flatter and outside off. Hope hangs back and punches it through cover for a single.
A dot now! Looped up, full and on off. Bonner strides and drives it towards point.
Full and on off. Bonner prods and defends it into the pitch.
Flighted, full and on leg. Bonner stays back and defends it back to the bowler.
Full and around off. Bonner blocks it out towards short cover. Just a single off it. A tidy over by Lasith Embuldeniya.

FOUR! Just eludes the fielder at square leg. Looped up, full and on middle. Hope steps across and looks to sweep it away. The ball takes the outside edge and goes towards deep square leg. Lakmal runs back from square leg and looks to grab the ball, but the ball lands safely in front of him, The ball races away to the fence. It was not an easy chance.
On the pads, Hope tucks it to mid-wicket for a quick single. Good running.
Full and on leg. Bonner nudges it to mid-wicket for another single. The batters are putting some pressure on the fielders.
On middle, Hope defends it out watchfully.
Full and on off. Hope skips down the track and works it towards long on for a single.
Darted on the pads, Bonner stays back and blocks it. He looks to be solid in his defense.

Three runs now! Full and on the pads, Hope stays back and tucks it through mid-wicket. Dimuth Karunaratne gives it a chase and he dives near the ropes to pull the ball back in play. The batters get enough time to run three.
Looped up, full and outside off. Bonner steps across and defends it out.
Flatter, around middle and leg. Bonner goes back and blocks it.
Full and on off. Bonner drives it to cover but straight to the man.
Full, and on leg. Bonner presses forward and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off. Bonner defends it into the pitch solidly. Just three runs off it.
Short and dragged down leg. Hope goes back, swivels and pulls it through square leg for a single.
Loopy ball, around off, the ball turns in. Bonner flicks it from the front of his pads to the leg side.
Tossed up, down leg. Bonner looks to flick but misses and the ball goes out off his pads.
Full and on middle. Bonner works it to the right of the bowler.
Flatter and on the pads, Bonner clips it through square leg for a single.
A dot to end the over! Flighted, full and on off. Hope comes forward and hits it back to the bowler on the bump though.
Floated, full and on off. Bonner pats it back to the bowler.
Looped up, full and on off. Bonner plays the inside-out drive and drives it to cover.
Tossed up, on off. Bonner goes back and defends it with the full face of the bat.
Short, outside off, with some away turn on it. Bonner hangs back and cuts it through point for a single.
Full and on off. Hope prods and blocks it out solidly.
Another tidy over by Lasith Embuldeniya! Looped up, outside off. Hope leaves it alone and lets it go to the keeper.

Sharp spin and bounce on this one! Floated, around middle. The ball turns in a long way. Bonner leaves it alone and lets it go down leg. Chandimal moves to his left and gathers the ball cleanly. He puts in a loud appeal but the umpire is unmoved.
Full, on leg. Bonner tucks it to square leg.
Full and on middle. Bonner clips it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, on middle and leg. Bonner flicks it to the leg side.
Looped up, around off. Bonner pushes it towards cover.
Quicker, full and on middle. Bonner defends it to short leg.
Tossed up, around middle. The ball turns away. Hope blocks it out.
Full and on off. Hope prods and defends it into the pitch.
Short, outside off. Hope cuts it to point for a single.
Loopy ball, outside off. Bonner leaves it alone for the keeper.

NOT OUT! Bonner survives. Loopy ball, full and outside off. Bonner looks to drive it to the off side. The ball bounces off the fielder at silly point and lobs to the man stationed behind him. The fielder dives in front and collects the ball. The Sri Lankan players put in an appeal but the umpire is unmoved. The umpires converge and decide to take it upstairs. The replays show that the ball had bounced before coming in contact with the player. The final decision is not out.
Flatter and on off. Bonner stays back and flicks it to the leg side for a single. Bonner retains the strike.
Floated, full and on middle. Bonner nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Two dots in a row now! Short and sliding down leg. Bonner swivels and looks to pull it away but misses.
Make that three! Looped up, on leg. Bonner defends it to short leg with soft hands.
Four dots on the trot! Looped up, full and on off. Bonner steps forward and pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, around middle and leg. Bonner looks to flick it away but misses. He gets hit on the pads. Mendis and the keeper, Dinesh Chandimal appeal but the umpire remains unmoved.
A maiden for Mendis. His fourth of the innings. Full and on off. Bonner defends it out solidly off the front foot.
Flatter ball, on off. Punched away.
Shorter ball, outside off. Hope plays it to cover.
Loopy ball, outside off. Hope blocks it from the crease.
Loopy ball, just outside off. Hope lools to block but the ball goes past the outside edge.
Full and outside off. Pushed past covers for one.
Shorter ball, on off. Bonner taps it from the crease.
Full and on the pads. Hope works it past leg slip and gets a couple of runs.
Full ball, on middle. Worked past mid-wicket for one.
Tossed up, around off. Bonner comes down the track and blocks it.
Shorter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, outside off. Bonner pushes it to cover.
Short ball, on middle. Bonner pulls it to deep square leg for one.
Loopy ball, outside off. Left alone.
Nicely tossed up, just outside off and turning away. Bonner works it to cover.
FOUR! Thick edge! Tossed up, outside off. Bonner looks to drive but gets the outside edge. The ball runs to the third man fence.
Shorter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, outside off. Bonner drives it nicely past cover for a couple.
Flighted delivery, quite wide and Bonner leaves it.

OUT! TAKEN! Straight to the man! A wicket against the run of play. Short ball, on off. Hope goes back and pulls it hard but straight to short square leg. Lakmal takes it with ease and a stand that was troubling the Lankan spinners is finally broken.
Howout: c Suranga Lakmal b Ramesh Mendis

Commentary: OUT! TAKEN! A golden duck for Chase and Mendis is on a hat-trick! This is why a stand is so important as it is not easy for the new man to bat under pressure. Tossed up, lands on off and turns back in. Chase looks to drive but gets the inside edge to short leg. Oshada Fernando takes it wicket ease!
Howout: c Oshada Fernando b Ramesh Mendis

Commentary: Mayers survives! An absolute ripper. Tossed up, lands just outside off. Mayers is forced to block at it but the ball turns away and goes past the outside edge.
Full and on the pads. Mayers looks to flick but gets hit on the pads. There is an appeal for LBW but the ball is going down leg most likely.
Loopy ball, lands outside off and turns away. Left alone.

OUT! TAKEN! WOW, WHAT AN OVER! A triple-wicket maiden for Mendis and the game has turned on its head! This one is a bit fuller, just outside off. Mayers gets forward to block but the ball turns away and takes the outside edge. Dhananjaya de Silva takes the simplest of catches at first slip!
Howout: c Dhananjaya de Silva b Ramesh Mendis

Commentary: Shorter ball, outside off. Cut away to cover.
Fuller ball, just outside off. Bonner expects the ball to turn away and leaves it. It goes straight but just past the off pole.
Full ball, on off. Pushed to cover.
Tossed up nicely, just outside off. Bonner gets to the pitch of the ball and blocks it.
Full and wider outside off. Bonner leaves it.
Full and on the pads. Bonner clips it past mid-wicket for a couple.
Full ball, on off. Mendis gets forward and blocks it.
Flatter ball, on the pads. Blocked out.
Shorter ball, on middle. Holder works it past square leg for one.
Bonner comes down the track and blocks this one.
Full and on the pads, a bit quicker too. Bonner works it to short leg.
Mendis lands it on off and gets it to turn back sharply. Bonner sees the ball go down the leg side.
Loopy ball, on off. Holder gets the outer half past silly point.
Full and on the pads. Worked to square leg.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Shorter ball, just outside off. Holder goes back to block and gets the inside edge on the pads.
Nicely driven to deep cover for a single.
Loppy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full ball, on off. Holder works it to mid-wicket.
Flatter ball, on off. Pushed down to long on for one.
Shorter ball, outside off. Bonner pulls it to deep mid-wicket for one.
FOUR! Full and on the pads. Bonner flicks it nicely to the fine leg fence.
Bonner comes down the track and blocks it.
Shorter ball, on middle. Worked to short leg.
Tossed up, just outside off. Holder looks to block but the ball turns away and goes past the outside edge.

OUT! TAKEN! Gets the outside edge this time! Flatter ball, on middle. Holder goes back and looks to block it out. But the ball turns away quite sharply and takes the outside edge. Dhananjaya de Silva takes it with ease at first slip and Sri Lanka move a wicket closer to a victory.
Howout: c Dhananjaya de Silva b Lasith Embuldeniya

Commentary: Shorter ball, on off. Da Silva plays it wide of short leg for one.
A single as this is pushed down to long off.
Full ball, on off. Blocked out.
Shorter ball, around off. Pushed to covers.
Shorter ball, on middle. Pulled down to deep square leg for one.
Full ball, on off. Hit down to long on for one.
Darted down the leg side. Bonner leaves it alone.
Bonner comes down the track and looks to work it away but gets hit on the pads.
Short ball, on off. Pulled to deep square leg for one.
Shorter ball, on off. Blocked out by Da Silva.
Around off. Bonner pushes it to cover.

OUT! DRAGGED ON! A long innings by Bonner comes to an end. Lasith Embuldeniya strikes and picks up his third wicket. Another one bites the dust and Sri Lanka are well and truly on top. This session has gone from bad to worse for the visitors. Tossed up, around off, too close to the body. Bonner goes back and looks to cut it away. The ball takes the inner half and strucks the off pole. Delight in the Sri Lankan camp.
Full and on middle. Roach prods and defends it solidly.
Looped up, outside off. Roach steps across and looks to defend it out. He gets beaten by the turn.
Tossed up, outside off. The ball grips and turns away. Roach steps across and looks to defend it out but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Play and a miss! Loopy ball, around off. The ball turns away sharply. Roach gets low and looks to sweep it away but misses.
LEG BYE! Floated, around middle and leg. Da Silva comes forward and looks to flick it away. The ball hits the top of the pad and lobs behind the leg slip fielder. They collect a leg bye.
FOUR! Nicely played. Short and sliding down leg. Roach stands back and pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary. He gets off the mark here.
A dot now! Full and on off. Roach gets his front leg across and defends it to cover.

NOT OUT! Loopy ball, full and on middle. Kemar Roach looks to sweep it away. The ball goes towards square leg. The batters cross for a single. Mendis thinks it has hit only the pads and he appeals for lbw but the umpire is unmoved. Dimuth Karunaratne opts to take the review. The UltraEdge shows the bat is involved and Roach survives. The batter gets a single.
Around off, da Silva drives it through covers for a couple.
Flatter and on leg. Joshua Da Silva blocks it out watchfully.
Tossed up, outside off, the ball turns away. Roach pats it towards point.
Full and on middle. Roach prods forward and defends it off the inner half to short leg.

FOUR! Nicely played. Full and on leg. Roach gets low and sweeps it towards deep square leg. Ramesh Mendis covers a lot of ground to his right. He puts in a dive to that side but fails to keep the ball in play.
Full and on off. Roach prods and defends it.
Outside off, left alone by Roach.
Full and on off. Roach pushes it towards extra cover.
Floated, full and on off. Da Silva defends it solidly.
On the pads, da Silva nudges it to the leg side.

Three dots in a row! Nice turn on this one! Loopy ball, outside off. The ball turns in sharply. Joshua Da Silva looks to defend it out but misses. He gets hit on his thighs. Ramesh Mendis puts in an appeal but the umpire is unmoved. Dimuth Karunaratne goes for the review. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. The Ball Tracker shows the ball is missing the wickets. Joshua Da Silva survives.
On leg, Joshua Da Silva defends it to the leg side.
FOUR BYES! Misses everyone. Tossed up, outside off. Joshua Da Silva steps forward and looks to drive it away but misses. The ball turns in and goes towards fine leg and into the fence.
Floated, around leg. Da Silva defends it out.
Flighted, full and outside off. The ball grips and turns away. Roach leaves it alone.
Full and on off. Roach pushes it to cover.
FOUR! Nicely played. Short and around off. Roach stays back and hits it through mid-wicket for a boundary.

OUT! LBW! Lasith Embuldeniya picks up his fourth wicket. Tossed up, around leg. The ball turns in. Kemar Roach gets low and looks to sweep it away but misses. He gets rapped on the pads. Lasith Embuldeniya appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Kemar Roach goes for the review. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. The Ball Tracker shows three reds and Roach has to trudge back to the pavilion. West Indies lose another wicket and also a review this time. Sri Lanka need two more wickets to win this.
Full and on leg. Permaul defends it out.
Around middle and leg. Permaul covers the stumps and flicks it to square leg for a single.
Full and on off. Permaul comes forward and defends it out.
On off. Permaul blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! Ramesh Mendis picks up his fifth wicket. He has been exceptional in this Test match. Floated, outside off. The ball turns in. Permaul gets inside the line and looks to flicks it away but misses. He gets rapped on his pads. Ramesh Mendis appeals and the umpire raises his dreaded finger. Veerasammy Permaul opts for the review. The UltraEdge shows no spike as the ball passes the blade. The Ball Tracker shows three reds and Permaul has to walk back. Jomel Warrican is the last man to come in.
DROPPED! Loopy ball, on off. Heaved to deep mid-wicket. Lasith Embuldeniya runs in from deep mid-wicket and dives but doesn't get to the ball.
Loopy ball, on off. Heaved past mid-wicket for one. Warrican is not going to hang around.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.

OUT! TAKEN! There comes the final wicket! Lasith Embuldeniya gets his five-wicket haul! Tossed up, outside off. Warrican looks to drive but gets the outside edge. Dhananjaya de Silva takes an easy catch at first slip! Sri Lanka win by 164 runs!
Howout: c Dhananjaya de Silva b Lasith Embuldeniya
